{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775882224764,"sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad444790017oX0f5A2PgKgBH","messageID":"msg_d7ad438fb0014HwIry40LNU5EG","sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882236244,"sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad446bc0018Jo6JR8rtY00eu","messageID":"msg_d7ad438fb0014HwIry40LNU5EG","sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_bae99d2239ef426186004aa0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod)\n\n## Summary\n\n为 AgentCube 项目的 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的 Go 单元测试，提高代码质量和可维护性。\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\n### Background\n\nrouter、store 和 picod 模块是 AgentCube 的核心组件：\n- **router**: 负责请求路由、负载均衡和流量管理\n- **store**: 负责状态存储、数据持久化和缓存管理\n- **picod**: 负责轻量级运行时环境管理和资源调度\n\n当前这些模块的测试覆盖不足，需要补充单元测试以确保代码质量。\n\n### Goal\n\n1. 为 router、store、picod 模块编写全面的单元测试\n2. 提高测试覆盖率到目标水平\n3. 确保关键业务逻辑的测试覆盖\n4. 建立持续测试的基础设施\n\n### Value\n\n- 提高代码质量，减少 regression\n- 为重构提供安全网\n- 提高开发者信心\n- 满足质量门禁要求\n\n---\n\n## Scope\n\n### In-Scope\n\n- pkg/router 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n- pkg/store 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n- pkg/picod 下的所有业务逻辑测试\n- 关键路径的单元测试\n- 边界条件和错误处理测试\n- 使用 fake client 或 mock 进行隔离测试\n\n### Out-of-Scope\n\n- 集成测试\n- 性能测试\n- E2E 测试\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. 单元测试通过率 100%\n2. 测试覆盖率目标 ≥ 70%\n3. 所有关键业务逻辑都有对应的测试用例\n4. 测试代码符合 Go 最佳实践\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Scope Analysis\n\n### 1. router 模块\n\n待分析...\n\n### 2. store 模块\n\n待分析...\n\n### 3. picod 模块\n\n待分析...\n\n---\n\n## Impact Analysis\n\n### Benefits\n\n1. **Increased Reliability**: Comprehensive test coverage reduces regression risk\n2. **Safe Refactoring**: Router, store, and picod operations can be safely modified\n3. **Documentation**: Tests serve as executable documentation\n4. **CI Confidence**: Full test suite enables confident continuous integration\n\n### Risks\n\n1. **Module Complexity**: Each module has different dependencies and interfaces\n2. **State Management**: Store module testing requires careful state isolation\n3. **External Dependencies**: Some components may require HTTP/gRPC mocking\n\n### Estimated Test Files\n\n- `router/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n- `store/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n- `picod/*_test.go` (new/enhance)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Plan\n\n1. **Phase 1**: Analyze existing code and identify testing gaps\n2. **Phase 2**: Implement router module tests\n3. **Phase 3**: Implement store module tests\n4. **Phase 4**: Implement picod module tests\n5. **Phase 5**: Coverage verification and improvements","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882236233,"end":1775882236241}}}}
