{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882267379,"sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad4a927001UEcNa81o7SCXZT","messageID":"msg_d7ad49c3d001VgEAxlAvuHxlb5","sessionID":"ses_2852c116fffet8svsJlHK9NUL6","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_f25341c805434ca98bd6b4bb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-039: Go 单元测试 (router/store/picod) - Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n> **Status:** ST-2 Proposal Complete\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis tasks.md defines atomic, independently verifiable tasks for implementing comprehensive Go unit tests for the router, store, and picod modules. Stage ST-2 (Proposal) is complete.\n\n---\n\n## Test File Status\n\nTBD - To be populated after code analysis\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: Code Analysis\n\n- [ ] **T-101** Analyze router module structure and identify testable functions\n- [ ] **T-102** Analyze store module structure and identify testable functions\n- [ ] **T-103** Analyze picod module structure and identify testable functions\n- [ ] **T-104** Document existing test coverage for each module\n- [ ] **T-105** Identify dependencies and mocking requirements\n\n### Phase 2: router 模块测试\n\n- [ ] **T-201** Create/enhance router test files\n- [ ] **T-202** Implement router test scenarios\n- [ ] **T-203** Add edge case tests\n- [ ] **T-204** Verify: All router tests pass\n\n### Phase 3: store 模块测试\n\n- [ ] **T-301** Create/enhance store test files\n- [ ] **T-302** Implement store test scenarios\n- [ ] **T-303** Add edge case tests\n- [ ] **T-304** Verify: All store tests pass\n\n### Phase 4: picod 模块测试\n\n- [ ] **T-401** Create/enhance picod test files\n- [ ] **T-402** Implement picod test scenarios\n- [ ] **T-403** Add edge case tests\n- [ ] **T-404** Verify: All picod tests pass\n\n### Phase 5: Integration & Coverage Verification\n\n- [ ] **T-501** Run all unit tests\n- [ ] **T-502** Generate coverage report\n- [ ] **T-503** Verify coverage ≥ 70% target\n- [ ] **T-504** Add any missing edge case coverage\n- [ ] **T-505** Run `go vet` on all test files\n- [ ] **T-506** Run `gofmt -s` on all test files\n\n---\n\n## Test Execution Commands\n\n```bash\n# Run router tests\ngo test ./pkg/router/... -v\n\n# Run store tests\ngo test ./pkg/store/... -v\n\n# Run picod tests\ngo test ./pkg/picod/... -v\n\n# Run all tests\ngo test ./pkg/... -v\n\n# Run with coverage\ngo test ./pkg/... -coverprofile=coverage.out -covermode=atomic\n\n# View coverage report\ngo tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Go 1.21+\n- `testing` package (stdlib)\n- Mocking utilities as needed\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. ✅ All test files created/enhanced as needed\n2. ✅ All delta-spec scenarios implemented\n3. ✅ Unit test pass rate: 100%\n4. ✅ Test coverage ≥ 70%\n5. ✅ Code passes `go vet` and `gofmt`\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Size: L - Large change requiring comprehensive testing across multiple modules\n- Tests should use table-driven test patterns for parameterized scenarios\n- Use appropriate mocking strategies based on module dependencies\n- Each task is independently verifiable and can be completed in any order within a phase","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-039/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775882267368,"end":1775882267376}}}}
